reviewText: Good old tv from  The 50s space operas lots of fun flash gordon &  Rocky jones  space rangers retro tv a good watch at a cheap price enjoy
If you like to watch the old Sci Fi's. this is the one to watch. Some are really terrible. Doesn't make them bad. If you compare them to Star Trek/Wars, then they are bad. Just enjoy.
